Recomended geometry 60x60

If you have the tahoma font I would recomend using these lines in the main gkrellmrc:
large_font = -ttf-tahoma-bold-r-normal-*-10-*-*-*-p-*-iso8859-1
normal_font = -ttf-tahoma-medium-r-normal-*-10-*-*-*-p-*-iso8859-1
small_font = -ttf-tahoma-medium-r-normal-*-9-*-*-*-p-*-iso8859-1

Also I like this as the contents of my ~/.eazel-engine-color (if you are running the Crux gtk theme):
#616e62

or
#879fa1

Lastly the ~/.gnome/Background:
[Default]
color1=#596055
color2=#9cac87
Enabled=true
simple=gradient
gradient=horizontal
wallpaper=none
wallpaperAlign=0
wallpapers=0
